.TH "BEEHIIV-POLLS-GET" "1" "Apr 2026" "beehiiv-cli" "Beehiiv CLI Manual"

.SH NAME
beehiiv-polls-get - Get poll OAuth Scope: polls:read


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbeehiiv polls get  [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Get poll OAuth Scope: polls:read

.PP
Retrieve detailed information about a specific poll belonging to a publication. Use \fBexpand[]=stats\fR for aggregate vote counts, or \fBexpand[]=poll_responses\fR for individual subscriber responses.

.PP
API path: /publications/{publicationId}/polls/{pollId}


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for get

.PP
\fB--query\fP=[]
	Add a repeatable query parameter in key=value form


